author: Little Chinese Everywhere
description:
In this video, we dive into the fascinating world of traditional Chinese medicine in Hangzhou. We visit one of the city’s most renowned clinics and experience several treatments firsthand, including cupping, acupuncture, and more. But the real question is, does it actually work?
Join us on this adventure into the old Chinese culture 🇨🇳

0:00 Intro 
1:35 Ginseng Coffee 
4:15 Chinese Medicine
6:56 Chinese Accupuncture
12:13 Chinese Cupping
